title: ELLIE ZEILER IS THE NEXT BIG INFLUENCER MEGASTAR — BFFs EP. 64
description:
Ellie Zeiler joins the pod to talk about her rise on TikTok, her future plans, and people saying she only got famous for looking like Charli D’Amelio. We rank TikTokkers by their fashion.
